#

Mushroom Quesadillas

25 min
$10
600 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyQuickSatisfying

Description

Savory mushroom quesadillas with melted cheese, perfect for a quick meal!

Ingredients

  • flour tortillas: 4
  • shredded cheese (cheddar or monterey jack): 1 cup
  • mushrooms (sliced): 2 cups
  • bell pepper (sliced): 1
  • onion (sliced): 1
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • sour cream (for serving): to taste
  • guacamole (for serving): to taste
